snippet: A 72-yard touchdown catch by Tom Crabtree and 176 total yards on the ground gave a much-needed boost to the Packers in their victory over the Cardinals.
abstract: Green Bay Packers defeat Arizona Cardinals, 31-17, to record their fourth consecutive victory.
lead_paragraph: A 72-yard touchdown catch by Tom Crabtree and 176 total yards on the ground gave a much-needed boost to the Packers in their victory over the Cardinals.

headline.seo: Green Bay Brings Back Ground Game in Victory Over Cardinals

headline.print_headline: The Packers Are Hobbled, Not Daunted
